            <thetext>At the moment it is not possible to use expressions like {@link ...} in the API documentation for @deprecated. The API Viewer interprets the expression as text, but in some cases it could be useful to have a link instead.

Here an example:

/**
 * Returns some value.
 * @return {Integer} Some value.
 * @deprecated Since X.X, please use the {@link #otherMethod} instead.
 */</thetext>
